text:
Windows behaviour can be set by using the following patch (it breaks Unix 
behaivour). I do not know what is the best way to determine whether the system 
is Windows based.
The patch:
369c369,370
<             int pos = env[i].indexOf('=');
---
>             String envstr=env[i];
>             int pos = envstr.indexOf('=');
